    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\ncold : hot :: active :\u00a0?\nA. activity\nB. excited\nC. lazy\nD. eager\n\nAnswer C. lazy\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nCold is the opposite of hot; similarly, active is the opposite of lazy.",
